  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509370/extras/ff013bec2f21c9c17ff37b724c46aa11.avif?t=1726892882\" width=512 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Cleric and Goblins\" is a thrilling VR action game featuring procedurally generated dungeons, a physics-based combat system, and intense loot collection. Your mission? To rescue the ever-unfortunate Cleric from a goblin-infested dungeon! But beware of the goblins' cunning traps at every turn. Battle your way through hordes of goblins, rescue the Cleric, and claim the ultimate loot in this hack-and-slash adventure! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unique Physics-Based Combat System:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weapons have weight and friction, and goblins are equally affected by physics. Swinging a sword lightly won’t suffice. <strong>Strike slowly, Precise force, and Deeply Stab the vital points!</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509370/extras/d0827f7c1a5393d34dbc6a1f33bbea93.poster.avif?t=1726892882\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509370/extras/d0827f7c1a5393d34dbc6a1f33bbea93.webm?t=1726892882\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509370/extras/d0827f7c1a5393d34dbc6a1f33bbea93.mp4?t=1726892882\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Rescue the Cleric!:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Your mission is to rescue the kidnapped Cleric!</strong> Navigate through goblin traps, save her, and safely escort her out of the dungeon! Remember, she is subject to physics too!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509370/extras/fa91cd710b2f1ffd5908c5b095151195.poster.avif?t=1726892882\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509370/extras/fa91cd710b2f1ffd5908c5b095151195.webm?t=1726892882\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509370/extras/fa91cd710b2f1ffd5908c5b095151195.mp4?t=1726892882\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Make Your Game Streaming Even More Engaging!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, you can import avatars in VRM0.0 format and play! Plus, it features a third-person camera that automatically captures cinematic angles, <strong>delivering immersive visuals to your audience!</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509370/extras/c96258663cf1d230f976a26c79cd8a57.poster.avif?t=1726892882\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509370/extras/c96258663cf1d230f976a26c79cd8a57.webm?t=1726892882\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509370/extras/c96258663cf1d230f976a26c79cd8a57.mp4?t=1726892882\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509370/extras/ff013bec2f21c9c17ff37b724c46aa11.avif?t=1726892882\" width=512 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Cleric and Goblins\" is a thrilling VR action game featuring procedurally generated dungeons, a physics-based combat system, and intense loot collection. Your mission? To rescue the ever-unfortunate Cleric from a goblin-infested dungeon! But beware of the goblins' cunning traps at every turn. Battle your way through hordes of goblins, rescue the Cleric, and claim the ultimate loot in this hack-and-slash adventure! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unique Physics-Based Combat System:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weapons have weight and friction, and goblins are equally affected by physics. Swinging a sword lightly won’t suffice. <strong>Strike slowly, Precise force, and Deeply Stab the vital points!</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509370/extras/d0827f7c1a5393d34dbc6a1f33bbea93.poster.avif?t=1726892882\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509370/extras/d0827f7c1a5393d34dbc6a1f33bbea93.webm?t=1726892882\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509370/extras/d0827f7c1a5393d34dbc6a1f33bbea93.mp4?t=1726892882\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Rescue the Cleric!:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Your mission is to rescue the kidnapped Cleric!</strong> Navigate through goblin traps, save her, and safely escort her out of the dungeon! Remember, she is subject to physics too!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509370/extras/fa91cd710b2f1ffd5908c5b095151195.poster.avif?t=1726892882\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509370/extras/fa91cd710b2f1ffd5908c5b095151195.webm?t=1726892882\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509370/extras/fa91cd710b2f1ffd5908c5b095151195.mp4?t=1726892882\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Make Your Game Streaming Even More Engaging!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, you can import avatars in VRM0.0 format and play! Plus, it features a third-person camera that automatically captures cinematic angles, <strong>delivering immersive visuals to your audience!</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509370/extras/c96258663cf1d230f976a26c79cd8a57.poster.avif?t=1726892882\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509370/extras/c96258663cf1d230f976a26c79cd8a57.webm?t=1726892882\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509370/extras/c96258663cf1d230f976a26c79cd8a57.mp4?t=1726892882\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
